                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "eaf83d20d39c4e879d30c",
                    "stepText": "Moving forward, choose the appropriate formula for the total orbital energy at perigee, which combines kinetic and potential energy. Identify the correct expression relating these quantities.",
